<div id="review_1154237409" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1154237409" />
    <a title="Debra " class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5032725-debra"><img alt="Debra " src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1627589236p2/5032725.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1154237409?book_show_action=true">Jan 03, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Debra " class="user" itemprop="url" name="Debra " href="/user/show/5032725-debra">Debra </a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1154237409" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1748596806317272686">the premise of this book was good. it sounded really interesting. unfortunately I was bored by most of it. I spent most of the day read it, in hopes it would get better. sadly, this book just did not work for me.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


